Class ClientDTO

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.model.account.AccountDTO
org.example.proyecto.model.client.ClientDTO
public class ClientDTO extends AccountDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for client information. This class extends the AccountDTO class and includes additional attributes specific to clients.
